{"tid":1719011,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實困曬係大學唔出黎係咩玩法","createTime":"2019-11-14T03:49:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T03:58:26.000Z","uid":10905,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6a8ca0ba2064420b893c579854617986ecc043f0","tid":1719011,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:49:23.000Z","msg":"中大果日我明<br />\n一失守曱甴就入曬去8964<br />\n但好啦曱甴輸左敗走<br />\n仲咁多人係入面做乜<br />\n<br />\n而加仲要嘉年華揸巴士<br />\n洗唔洗打埋邊爐打埋兵乓波<br />\n唔只cu<br />\nBu cu poly又係咁玩死守白白送頭<br />\n結果出面冇撚曬人<br />\n<br />\n你地口口聲聲話冇曱甴就冇衝突<br />\n但就唔識倒番轉諗 冇人叫曱甴打空氣咩<br />\n<br />\n釋放各位手足啦好嗎今日已經明顯少左人啦"},{"pid":"a673b3509a99c9e0b65e34bffc4c501af1cc17e2","tid":1719011,"uid":82955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:51:12.000Z","msg":"[文宣升級&mdash;要追上前線行動呀！]<br />\n解鎖新職業 &mdash; 郵差叔叔，速遞員！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1717313\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1717313</a><br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，手足，借個位，認同請幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n發生好多事，好多怨案，令我地好嬲好嬲。但文宣一定要做足做好，我地係為正義而戰，我地從來都唔係暴徒！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/arAivP6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FarAivP6.png&h=a9a1a627&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zSLZfgM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzSLZfgM.jpg&h=20bdb60e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d017c5bceaddac2fc7d779b0884bbfa67e3f0197","tid":1719011,"uid":55919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:51:38.000Z","msg":"堵塞主要幹道，強制罷工"},{"pid":"67a1eb707cd21180f81d71d99a1e87bcc715e493","tid":1719011,"uid":210296,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:55:56.000Z","msg":"今朝六點半已經吹左雞出城架喇<br />\n而家守城既多數都係中大人"},{"pid":"b2595e82fc586ab9ac329e470dfa9bbb16ebc9e4","tid":1719011,"uid":284630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:58:26.000Z","msg":"用校巴/家長車帶中大物資出去支援開花, 接發夢手足入校園暫避,休息<br />\n到時中大就有一層新既抗爭意義, 政府又唔可以坐視不理<br />\n當然最危險係運輸中途俾狗截擊"}]}